\tab The primary resource is the Resource Unit.  The RU is used to jump from one map to the next, upgrade unitsThe RU can be converted into secondary resources: Supplies, Ammo, and fuel.  When converting RU's supplies should be cheaper than ammo, and ammo, cheaper than fuel.  Supply represents things like oxygen, food, and water.  Supply is depleted at the end of every turn.  Ammo is used up every time the unit attacks.  Fuel is used up every time the unit moves.  Larger units may have their fuel decremented each turn to simulate the larger energy requirement for life support, etc.  It will allow the larger ships to be more powerful tactically wile gimping them strategically. }
